\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"schoolchildren\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"Emily Ford\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"their older brothers\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"John\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"Ed\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grange School\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given that half that boatwould go on tobecomeOlympicmedallists atParis 2024, you'd assume that they would have been absolutely unbeatable, and yet all the talent did not quite come together.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that half\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"tobecomeOlympicmedallists\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"all the talent\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emily recalled: \\\"We have been out with our two older brothers in the four before and it wasn't very good from memory.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Emily\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"our two older brothers\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"memory\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were no arguments but it did not quite gel.\\\"\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no arguments\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"quite gel\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thankfully for the duo, that was absolutely not the caseon the final day of the Olympic regattaat the Stade Nautique in Vaires-sur-Marne, as Emily was part of the women's eight that won bronze before older brother Tom helped the men's eight to gold 20 minutes later.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother_Tom\", \"score\": 0.9999212993145693, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"brother Tom\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother_Tom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother_Tom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the duo\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the caseon\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic regattaat\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade Nautique\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"Vaires\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"sur-Marne\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"Emily\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In doing so, they made history, the first brother and sister to win medals at the same Olympic Games forTeam GBsince 1908 - matching the exploits of archers William and Lottie Dod in London 116 years ago.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lottie Dod\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\"}, {\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9657691955666272, \"rank\": 0.03544408309146978, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"the first brother\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"sister\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"the same Olympic Games forTeam GBsince\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"the exploits\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"archers\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"William\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And both siblings were quick to pay tribute to the part their parents, Paul and Christine, had played in getting them to this point.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.740007813330513e-23, \"text\": \"Christine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both siblings\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the part\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"Paul\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom said: \\\"Mum and Dad did not push us into anything but they encouraged us to try all sports.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"Mum\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"Dad\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"all sports\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They wanted us to follow our dreams and do what we enjoy.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"our dreams\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That happened to berowingand they have supported for us ever since we made the decision that we wanted to do it full time.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, they are the reason we were on the start line and the podium today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom, 31, was preparing for his Olympic final as Emily, 29, brought home bronze behind Romania and Canada, alongside Heidi Long, Rowan McKellar, Holly Dunford, Lauren Irwin, Eve Stewart, Hattie Taylor and Annie Campbell-Orde.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9992965055242021, \"rank\": 0.0006504342997543836, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1996, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9413985346831004, \"rank\": 0.058227832244115006, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\", \"score\": 0.9842438778447239, \"rank\": 0.016008253373584694, \"text\": \"Heidi\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\"}, {\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowan_McKellar\", \"score\": 0.9999972294696998, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rowan McKellar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowan_McKellar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowan_McKellar\"}, {\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\", \"score\": 0.6823659817803885, \"rank\": 0.46548854961033553, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\"}, {\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9959082255935424, \"rank\": 0.004108495130042156, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Irwin\"}, {\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eve Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"score\": 0.9999956150464374, \"rank\": 4.06115185701777e-06, \"text\": \"Annie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic final\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"Emily\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"home bronze\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"Hattie Taylor\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tom made sure to find out what had happened before his own bid for an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"his own bid\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I asked the cox Harry [Brightmore], because I could not see the big screen.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cox Harry\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"[Brightmore\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"the big screen\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said they got a bronze.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I kept it internal.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When you are out there on the water, you know you have a job to do.\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what we train for.\\\"\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the entire family starting rowing from an early age, Emily is the first to admit that she did not take to it straight away.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the entire family\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"Emily\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But having conquered her fear of the water, and with the support of her older brother, she has shown that slow starters can come good.\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fear\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"her older brother\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"slow starters\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I was definitely petrified of falling in.\\\"\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom joked: \\\"If you have seen her in a swimming pool, you will understand why.\\\"\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimming pool\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I remember going into a boat for the first time and I went straight into a bush, so I did not start as a natural.\\\"\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a boat\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"a bush\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once she had got to grips with it, the support of an older brother proved invaluable, even up to the final preparations for this regatta.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"grips\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"an older brother\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"the final preparations\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"this regatta\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"We know each other inside and out.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have pretty much followed the same path, so we have had support from each other all the way.\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same path\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been with each other through the ups and the downs.\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ups\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"the downs\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's definitely an advantage, the other day we did not have a good session and I spoke to Tom and he said do not worry about it, it will come together and it did.\\\"\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"a good session\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory of the men, where Ford was joined by Sholto Carnegie, Rory Gibbs, Morgan Bolding, Jacob Dawson, Charlie Elwes, Tom Digby and James Rudkin, was hugely impressive.\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3518, \"end\": 3522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Motor_Company\", \"score\": 0.9999851298971982, \"rank\": 1.2409269218146336e-05, \"text\": \"Ford\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Motor_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Motor_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 3537, \"end\": 3552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sholto_Carnegie\", \"score\": 0.9999999691917769, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sholto Carnegie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sholto_Carnegie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sholto_Carnegie\"}, {\"begin\": 3554, \"end\": 3558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\", \"score\": 0.9999990493683952, \"rank\": 9.50626141069643e-07, \"text\": \"Rory\", \"type